### ─── Users (Admin) ───

### List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create moderator (admin creates account with email + password)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "moderator@example.com",
  "username": "moderator1",
  "password": "Moderator123!",
  "role": "MODERATOR"
}

### Create uploader directly (admin creates account)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "uploader@example.com",
  "username": "uploader1",
  "password": "Uploader123!",
  "role": "UPLOADER"
}

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Change user role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "MODERATOR"
}

### Change user status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "SUSPENDED"
}
